events.content:
Perform an authorized red team assessment against the local lab target.
Start with reconnaissance to identify open ports, running services, and potential vulnerabilities.
If low-risk vulnerabilities are found, attempt controlled exploitation for initial access.
Document every step and summarize findings with remediation suggestions.
